1. Ona ima *slab* vid bez naočara. (She has *weak* eyesight without glasses.)
2. Njeni argumenti su *slabi* i nedovoljni. (Her arguments are *weak* and insufficient.)
3. Volim da jedem *slabe* začinjene jela. (I like to eat *mildly* spicy food.)
4. Čula sam da će sutra biti *slaba* kiša. (I heard that there will be *light* rain tomorrow.)
5. Moja majka se oseća *slabo* danas. (My mother feels *unwell* today.)
6. Njegova lojalnost je bila *slaba* i brzo se promenio. (His loyalty was *weak* and he changed quickly.)
7. Oni su izgradili *slabu* kuću koja se lako ruši. (They built a *flimsy* house that is easily destructible.)
8. Sviđa mi se tvoj novi friz. Samo je *slabo* ofarban. (I like your new haircut. It's just *poorly* dyed.)
9. Njegov uspeh u školi je *slab* zbog nedostatka motivacije. (His success in school is *poor* due to a lack of motivation.)
10. Jako je *slab* vjetar danas, možemo jedriti. (The wind is very *light* today, we can go sailing.)